Class CardReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.CardReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class CardReader
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Author:
    Brian Wehrle, Patrick Maley Class Description: CardReader creates and Accountcollection object to determine whether or not the login information in the JukeBox controller is in the hashmap. If so it returns true and sets the currentAccount to true.
